text:
Even though this library is not as big as Woodlands and Jurong East Regional Libraries, it still carries plenty of books and itâ€™s spacious enough too with plenty of comfortable seats.
I also like the more relaxed vibe here with plenty of plants.

Library collection map for free and  if you borrow books, earn points exchange for bug cards using vending machine. There are a total of 100 types of bug cards.

For details information, ask librarian for assistance.
The library has a dedicated children's section that is welcoming, engaging and safe. The kid's area is designed with bright colors, comfy seating and fun decorations.
Tried to collect book bugs. Before 5pm the librarian already said the bugs are out of stock....what a disappointment for the kids

Love to study here because it's much less crowded than other libraries and easy to book seats. coffee shop opposite is rly convenient to hv lunch and take a study break. Many of the libraries nowadays are renovated and "modern", nice to have an older nostalgic library
